      "instruction": "<p>Preheat the oven to 220°C/ 200°C (fan)/ gas 7</p><p>Peel and chop (or grate) your <strong>garlic</strong></p><p>Peel and finely chop your <strong>brown onion[s]</strong></p><p>Drain and rinse your <strong>butter beans</strong></p>",
