    {
      "instruction": "<p>Transfer the <strong>creamy</strong> <strong>butter bean, squash & sage filling</strong> to an <strong>oven-proof dish </strong>(reserve the pan) and carefully arrange the <strong>potato discs </strong>over the top</p><p>Season with a pinch of <strong>salt</strong> and put the dish in the oven for 25-30 min – this is your <strong>butter bean, squash & sage hotpot</strong></p>",
