    {
      "instruction": "<p>While the hotpot is in the oven, wash your <strong>spring greens </strong>then pat it dry with kitchen paper</p><p>Rip the leaves off your <strong>spring greens</strong>, discard the tough stalks, then layer the leaves over each other, roll them up and slice into thin strips</p>",
